              <p>We are a small group of artists within a larger associated artistic community. Our members are students, alumni, and faculty. Hailing from a wide array of disciplines, we come together to celebrate the arts and letters. Outside of the Signet, we uphold our shared appreciation by contributing to and supporting the arts.

                For 150 years, the Signet Society has functioned as a gathering place for creative thinkers and their mentors—a forum for conversation and collaboration that lets those who occupy the space engage with and learn from one another. </p>
