              <p>January 1, 2020: The Signet will be closed for the spring semester in compliance with Harvard University’s COVID-19 guidance and Harvard College’s prohibition on indoor gatherings, as well as the ongoing Governor's Orders on indoor gatherings. We will continue to prioritize the health and safety of our students and staff, and look forward to welcoming you back to lunch when it is safe to do so. For the time being, we are excited to build new community initiatives remotely. If you are a current Signet member or alum who’d like to be involved in planning these initiatives, please reach out to the Membership Office — we’ll be delighted to hear from you. </p>
               <hr>
